# GROUP LEARNING FEATURES BRAINSTORMING (REALISTIC WORKFLOW)
Date: 2025-01-31

## CURRENT STATUS ✅
- ✅ Individual quiz system from video content (DONE)
- ✅ Group quiz functionality during video listening (EXISTING)

## ACTUAL LEARNING WORKFLOW
**Real-world process:**
1. Teacher shares YouTube screen
2. Group reads questions together beforehand
3. Group listens to video together
4. Group takes quiz individually but simultaneously

