- Real-time member join status
- Simultaneous quiz start for all members
- Group results comparison after completion

**Post-Quiz Activities:**
- Group results leaderboard
- Compare member answers side by side
- Simple group celebration for achievements
- Session completion tracking

### 3. COMPETITIVE ELEMENTS (Simplified)
**Group Competition:**
- Member ranking within group
- Group completion streaks
- Simple achievement badges
- Weekly group progress summary

### 4. GROUP ANALYTICS (Essential Only)
**Performance Dashboard:**
- Group completion rates
- Member participation consistency
- Average group scores over time
- Most challenging questions for group

### 5. MINIMAL SOCIAL FEATURES
**Group Communication:**
- Session scheduling and reminders
- Group announcements from admin

